fe4456235e37fa64fb49e099e75e9c6d.data:
4Geeks Academy offers various coding bootcamps, including a Cybersecurity Bootcamp that lasts 16 weeks. Classes are 3 live online sessions per week, with up to 18 students per class. This program covers Windows, Linux, cloud security, penetration testing, and data loss prevention. 

Students can choose between English and Spanish courses and receive an official completion certificate. No prior experience is required, with classes taught in the language of the campus. 

For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity stop

f10fb40f21d5020dbe900489103a19f4.data:
4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week AI Machine Learning Engineering course. 
You'll learn Python, SQL, and statistics, and become proficient in creating predictive models with Pandas and Numpy.
 Master industry-standard tools and develop your own A.I. projects.
Instructors include Sayyed Nezhadi, PhD in Artificial Intelligence, and Manuel Mena, Senior Data Scientist.
Choose from English or Spanish for the syllabus.
More information: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning stop
